You can view a bunch of them on <a href="http://www.instagram.com/wesleydonehue">Instagram</a> with #HarlowesHats.

Every year on Harlowe’s birthday, we release a special beer in his honor. Harlowe’s Hats is a peanut butter and banana porter because, well, his favorite snack was always peanut butter and banana.

Even though Harlowe has seventeen years until he can try his special brew, you can have as much as you want, hang out with our family, AND celebrate Star Wars Day all at once!

The festivities pop off at 5:00 pm on Friday. We will be there until at least 7:00 pm. Me, Harlowe, Tennyson, the Frothy team and some of the Push team will be dressed up. If I’m lucky I’ll even get Elizabeth to dress up.
<h5>If I’m real lucky, I’ll get Elizabeth to dress up as slave Leia. ?</h5>
<p class="p1">—W</p>
